data.description: Beautiful 55 and up Community with only 14 homes.   Originally built for Veterans now open to the public.   Appealing small community centered around a beautiful flag pole and benches.   Planned in a Florida cottage “pocket community” design, the village has an old-time feel, where front porch sitting and knowing your neighbors is encouraged. The location is beautifully situated on Lake Enola, with walkable access to downtown and near the local bus line. Each unit is ADA compliant, energy efficient to the highest standards, and sustainable.   Come visit our quaint town of Umatilla and make this your Home.
